{"tid":1889450,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎】TVB化妝師困鑽石公主號今早確診 李寶安：正於日本接受治療","createTime":"2020-02-20T15:48:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T15:48:43.000Z","uid":349930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"886ed34d37328bd8e48bc145cd23aa272b0e9fd8","tid":1889450,"uid":349930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T15:48:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200220/LQFRAUGLE4C7PCVU7GX74B2I2A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200220%2FLQFRAUGLE4C7PCVU7GX74B2I2A%2F&d=1mfmSgVVN%2FWy7xf%2FaESqF%2FQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=e8124e68\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200220%2FLQFRAUGLE4C7PCVU7GX74B2I2A%2F&h=d1ed7eb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200220/LQFRAUGLE4C7PCVU7GX74B2I2A/</a><br />\n李寶安回應《蘋果》：「鑽石公主號上其中一名確診女患者為本台化妝師，她今曰（20日）通知公司說早上被確診，現正於日本接受治療。她自1月25日開始休假至今。」<br />\n其後李寶安亦向職藝員同事發出電郵，表示公司今日收到美術分部一位化粧同事通知，表示自己是鑽石公主號的乘客，今早確診受到感染，需要留在日本接受治療，公司祝願她早日康復，亦提醒同事們必須保持警覺，加強個人衛生，齊心抗疫。"}]}